rComments: Probably one of the most boring classes I've ever taken..bring crosswords and/or books to lecture..also, her voice is really annoying.  Overall, the class wasn't bad..the review sessions help A LOT!

The curve for this class is awesome, a B is 70, it doesn't get better, some people I know got a D on the first couple exams, then a B on the final exam, and Still pulled of a B, the best gen ed I took so far!
Not an easy blow off gen ed
great teacher. very clear, helpful, and the lecture notes are the tests exactly.
